snippet.title: Atelier Ryza 2: Lost Legends & the Secret Fairy - TGS 2020 Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
"If we are together, nothing is impossible!”

An all-new trailer for #AtelierRyza2 has been revealed at #TGS2020, featuring the theme song 'Somewhen, Somewhere...' by Clammbon

Learn more: https://www.koeitecmoamerica.com/ryza2/
